American Can Co &lt;AC.N> is issuing a 150mln dlr convertible eurobond due April 22, 2002 carrying anindicated coupon of 5-1/2 to 5-7/8 pct priced at par, leadmanager Morgan Stanley International said.    Terms will be set this week with a conversion premium of 25to 28 pct. The bond is available in denominations of 1,000 and10,000 dlrs and be listed in Luxembourg.    There is no call for three years, subsequently at par plusthe coupon, declining by equal amounts per annum until 1997.    Fees comprise 1-1/2 pct selling concession and one pctmanagement and underwriting combined. REUTER&#3;